name: CrossFilter
description: Contains methods and constructors used to work with information about a cross filter.

getcriteria().name: getCriteria
getcriteria().description: Returns information about how to filter the relatedEntity. Describes the subset of the relatedEntity which the primary entity is evaluated against.

getincludesobject().name: getIncludesObject
getincludesobject().description: Returns true if primary object has a relationship with the relatedEntity, otherwise returns false.

getprimaryentityfield().name: getPrimaryEntityField
getprimaryentityfield().description: Returns the name of the object on which the cross filter is evaluated.

getrelatedentity().name: getRelatedEntity
getrelatedentity().description: Returns name of the object that the primaryEntityField is evaluated against—the right-hand side of the cross filter.

getrelatedentityjoinfield().name: getRelatedEntityJoinField
getrelatedentityjoinfield().description: Returns the name of the field used to join the primaryEntityField and relatedEntity.

setcriteria(list<reports.reportfilter>).name: setCriteria
setcriteria(list<reports.reportfilter>).description: Specifis how to filter the relatedEntity. Relates the primary entity with a subset of the relatedEntity.

setincludesobject(boolean).name: setIncludesObject
setincludesobject(boolean).description: Specifies whether objects returned have a relationship with the relatedEntity (true) or not (false).

setprimaryentityfield(string).name: setPrimaryEntityField
setprimaryentityfield(string).description: Specifies the name of the object on which the cross filter is evaluated.

setrelatedentity(string).name: setRelatedEntity
setrelatedentity(string).description: Specifies the name of the object that the primaryEntityField is evaluated against—the right-hand side of the cross filter.

setrelatedentityjoinfield(string).name: setRelatedEntityJoinField
setrelatedentityjoinfield(string).description: Specifies the name of the field used to join the primaryEntityField and relatedEntity.
